    <item>
      <title>高盛表示，即使市场看起来“不稳定”，股市也会上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/goldman-says-stocks-to-rise-even-if-markets-look-shaky-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛资产配置研究主管克里斯蒂安·穆勒-格利斯曼(Christian Mueller-Glissmann)表示，市场看起来“不稳定”，但正增长、通胀下降和央行降息预期意味着股市将取得进展。 “增长良好，收益率最终会达到平衡，你会得到一些削减，”他告诉彭博电视台。 “所有这些都应该使股市稳定并取得进展。”]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-16/goldman-says-stocks-to-rise-even-if-markets-look-shaky-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 09:38:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>押注美联储推迟降息，美元有望创年内最佳表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/usd-dollar-heads-for-best-run-in-year-in-bet-on-fed-delaying-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对美国利率将在更长时间内保持高位的预期不断增强，促使投资者纷纷买入美元，美元即将迎来一年多来的最大涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-16/usd-dollar-heads-for-best-run-in-year-in-bet-on-fed-delaying-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Apr 2024 09:31:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
